%% Model Registry - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.2/model-registry.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/Pipeline/SDK)
    participant IstioGW as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MRService as model-registry-service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant MySQL as MySQL<br/>3306/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as model-registry-controller
    participant CSI as mr-storage-initializer
    participant ModelStore as Model Storage<br/>(S3/OCI) 443/TCP
    participant CatalogSvc as model-catalog<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Browser as Browser
    participant BFF as model-registry-ui BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,MySQL: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
    Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    IstioGW->>MRService: Forward (mTLS)<br/>Istio AuthorizationPolicy
    MRService->>MySQL: INSERT model metadata<br/>Auth: username/password
    MySQL-->>MRService: OK
    MRService-->>IstioGW: 201 Created
    IstioGW-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over K8sAPI,MRService: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>MRService: PUT /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/inference_services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    MRService-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over CSI,ModelStore: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
    Note right of CSI: KServe triggers init container
    CSI->>MRService: GET model artifact URI<br/>model-registry:// resolution
    MRService-->>CSI: Artifact location (S3/OCI URL)
    CSI->>ModelStore: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: Storage credentials, TLS 1.2+
    ModelStore-->>CSI: Model files

    Note over CatalogSvc,HF: Flow 4: Catalog Model Browsing
    Client->>CatalogSvc: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/models<br/>mTLS (Istio)
    CatalogSvc->>PG: Query catalog metadata<br/>Auth: username/password
    PG-->>CatalogSvc: Catalog results
    CatalogSvc->>HF: GET model metadata (leader only)<br/>Auth: API Key (optional)
    HF-->>CatalogSvc: Model metadata
    CatalogSvc-->>Client: JSON catalog response

    Note over Browser,BFF: Flow 5: UI Model Management
    Browser->>BFF: HTTP request<br/>Auth: user_token/internal
    BFF->>MRService: Proxy API call<br/>mTLS (Istio), SA Token
    MRService-->>BFF: API response
    BFF->>CatalogSvc: Proxy catalog call<br/>mTLS (Istio), SA Token
    CatalogSvc-->>BFF: Catalog response
    BFF->>K8sAPI: Kubernetes API call<br/>HTTPS, SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>BFF: K8s response
    BFF-->>Browser: HTML/JSON response
